Opeyemi Falegan, ex-lover of popular actress, Nkechi Blessing has appreciated God for a sound mental health on his birthday. Falegan expressed gratitude to his maker for granting him happiness, peace of mind among other things. He described the above as priceless gifts though little but worthy of being celebrated. “I might not be the richest person in the world or the world’s president but I have happiness, peace of mind, and most importantly the gift of life.   Regina Onuoha carpets Yul Edochie over polygamous post     Why infidelity of Lagos girls hurts more – Tochi     Polygamy has blessed my family – Yul Edochie   “Thank you, God, for blessing me with such priceless gifts. On my birthday, I celebrate these little but priceless things,” he wrote. Falegan and his former beau, NBS, fell apart in April in what many would consider messy breakup saw them go at each other with several accusations and counter accusations. The duo opened can of worms for weeks unending following news of their crashed relationship barely a year after finding love in each other’s arms.